name: number-and-membership-to-existing-labor-organizations-by-type-of-labor-organization
notes:
This dataset contains the number and membership of existing labor organizations in the Philippines classified by type of labor organization from 1980 to 2012. Note: Note:  Starting 2002, membership of local/independent unions includes membership of federations/labor centers.		
year 2010 to 2011- Pleminary,	
year 1989  As of Federation Number- Federation cancelled (AFLU).		
year 2011 Local/ Independent Unions-  Includes 3 industry unions.		
Public Sector Unions- Registration of Public Sector Unions started only in September 1987.
